author: Cleo Abram
description:
Breaking news! This image could show life on Mars…. 

It was taken by the Perseverance rover in a place that was likely filled with water but dried up over time. The rover took a sample of the rock and here’s what it found… 

To find out what happens next, subscribe!  

#shorts #mars #science #space #NASA
title: New Sign of Life On Mars (Really)
